## 0.1.0 (2026-07-08)

- Initial Cloudron release based on OmniRoute v3.8.46
- Cloudron OIDC integration for single sign-on
- Redis addon for rate limiting
- Local storage addon for SQLite persistence
- Health check endpoint configured
- 237+ providers, 90+ free tiers
- Token compression (RTK + Caveman)
- Auto-fallback and combo routing
- MCP Server (94 tools)
- A2A Protocol support
